{"tid":1114933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"11場10球，基奧特成為車路士歐戰賽場進球數第一人","createTime":"2019-04-18T19:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:54:22.000Z","uid":1369,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c55a18216a45096e588c73a5468b8659dcfec804","tid":1114933,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T19:37:53.000Z","msg":"在現在正在進行的歐霸盃0.25決賽第二回合，基奧特攻入了車路士本場比賽的第三球，憑藉此球，基奧特本賽季歐霸盃進球數達到10個。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xo5MdHf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxo5MdHf.png&h=e202a70b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基奧特也成為了車路士歐戰歷史上第一位單賽季打進10球的球員。從2009到2010賽季開始，在歐戰賽場上進球達到兩位數的球員只有5位，他們分別是法卡奧（2次）、朱施比-羅斯、亨特拉爾、阿度里斯和基奧特。"},{"pid":"96a6685527fb99102d1e5fdeef71d6a74042067d","tid":1114933,"uid":235174,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:25:11.000Z","msg":"真係唔知應該傷心定開心好"},{"pid":"354bc8fd9f2710c347a971f8c9cbc0f3e9f56632","tid":1114933,"uid":155133,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔識貨既教練食屎啦"},{"pid":"555660be5baaf73c53dae54ab11983af64446fb8","tid":1114933,"uid":38461,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:47:23.000Z","msg":"0.25決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8700dbe2a03a684f5ee20d8b16a7cfc406729cbe","tid":1114933,"uid":105121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T20:54:12.000Z","msg":"歐戰=歐霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52c74406f0cf2819e30eb610e531694a84b3d08","tid":1114933,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T23:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52a9bdba866ff9f64718fe7423123b7d18bbe44","tid":1114933,"uid":66178